{"tid":2454402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<科學>:模型模擬的結果顯示，當時的武漢人處在被病毒持續的轟炸中","createTime":"2021-03-20T08:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T09:35:09.000Z","uid":294518,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb5be21a9f7f2c47a42464f9544735dc37207e9","tid":2454402,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:14:38.000Z","msg":"《科學》剛剛發表的研究成果，通過模型推測新冠病毒疫情最有可能出現在2019年10月中旬至11月中旬<br />\n<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2021/03/17/science.abf8003.full\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2Fscience.abf8003.full&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDIhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=a29e69c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2021/03/17/science.abf8003.full</a><br />\n<br />\n文章的作者Wertheim接受採訪時說：<br />\n1，很意外，模型模擬的結果顯示，模擬100次2019年的疫情，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">病毒在三分之二的情況下都會自行消亡，</span></span>不會引起全球瘟疫<br />\n<br />\n2，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">然而最終出現的全球瘟疫表明，當時的武漢人處在被病毒持續的轟炸中</span></span></strong>（&ldquo;humans are constantly being bombarded&rdquo;）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CpEKcyc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCpEKcyc.png&h=ca122186&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3c4a6457d2cc73c4fd8cac25c0d17ac815a376c","tid":2454402,"uid":294518,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"很大概率上，武漢初期是有大規模，高劑量，地毯式的病毒轟炸（bombarded），才可能引發後來的全球大流行，這也許還原了當時的武漢處在怎樣一種狀況"},{"pid":"cbeed9ca209ebed305f5cb7b803baa3217b3cbe1","tid":2454402,"uid":324629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:16:35.000Z","msg":"「武漢肺炎」走唔甩，支那播毒責無旁貸"},{"pid":"e461728458cb88b35c1bdeff7f3364e22eaeab8e","tid":2454402,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:17:57.000Z","msg":"鄰國持續排放病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla